'''第72届[[威尼斯影展|威尼斯影展]]'''於2015年9月2日至9月12日（當地時間）在[[義大利|義大利]][[威尼斯|威尼斯]]舉行<ref name="Venice2015">{{cite web |url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/72nd-festival/ |title=Venice International Film Festival |accessdate=25 January 2015 |work=Venice |archive-date=2015-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150406205546/http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/72nd-festival/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。並在影展期間首映一部[[费德里柯·费里尼|费德里柯·费里尼]]的《[[阿瑪柯德|阿瑪柯德]]》修復版<ref name="Amarcord">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2015/film/global/venice-fest-to-bow-freshly-restored-copy-of-federico-fellinis-amarcord-1201519661/ |title=Venice Fest To Bow Freshly Restored Copy Of Federico Fellini’s ‘Amarcord’ |accessdate=15 June 2015 |work=Variety |archive-date=2015-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150623214240/http://variety.com/2015/film/global/venice-fest-to-bow-freshly-restored-copy-of-federico-fellinis-amarcord-1201519661/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。官方宣布由[[巴塔薩·科馬庫|巴塔薩·科馬庫]]所執導的《[[聖母峰_(電影)|聖母峰]]》為本屆開幕片<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/07/baltasar-kormakurs-everest-venice-film-festival-universal-working-title-1201472041/ |title=Baltasar Kormákur’s ‘Everest’ To Open Venice Film Festival |author=Ali Jaafar |date=8 July 2015 |accessdate=8 July 2015 |work=Deadline Hollywood |archive-date=2017-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170711103945/http://deadline.com/2015/07/baltasar-kormakurs-everest-venice-film-festival-universal-working-title-1201472041/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[委内瑞拉|委内瑞拉]]导演[[洛伦佐·维加斯|洛伦佐·维加斯]]执导的处女作《[[来自远方_(电影)|来自远方]]》爆冷夺[[金狮奖|金狮奖]]，成为继[[李安|李安]]的《[[断背山|断背山]]》后又一部获得金狮奖的同志题材电影<ref >{{cite web |url=http://ent.163.com/15/0913/05/B3CD32FI00031H2L.html |language= |title=《来自远方》爆冷夺金狮 《断背山》获奖十年后 |publisher=网易娱乐 |date=2015-09-13 |accessdate= |archive-date=2015-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150918003246/http://ent.163.com/15/0913/05/B3CD32FI00031H2L.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

